id":1546051,"uid":78122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:40:56.000Z","msg":"沒有國泰 還有民安"},{"pid":"6f92ec2fa76fbd30d50fda9a9a9dd8ede6c2c45d","tid":1546051,"uid":4346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"Tommy同大學都connect到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e6f9cd2a81e3671e832992267dc9f5a50af387","tid":1546051,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:42:30.000Z","msg":"何事我會妒忌我會擔心魔鬼搶走你"},{"pid":"30b7820a27f8b17cb1fc6feee2f87204ec74e9e7","tid":1546051,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"tommy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17826d7911192bfb2f3725a7c999be64e8827fae","tid":1546051,"uid":292075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從個心型出黎"},{"pid":"8a80090e520368b0337c506d55ef0a957ddfcb23","tid":1546051,"uid":65530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0967f17c10b99aaf5eb175b9ea7779d80a7e1719","tid":1546051,"uid":172627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:02:03.000Z","msg":"終於係大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d8a0d2586ed8fe040ffd7eacd3a9ea0c8818c9","tid":1546051,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"樹中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f366ea0adee35f11870320de478e5857e5b958","tid":1546051,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>中英聯合聲明的謬誤</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若果一件物件是從來未曾擁有過，拿到手上是談不上「恢復」及「收回」的。同樣道理，1997年前中華人民共和國從來未曾對香港行使過主權，如何談得上「恢復行使主權」？中華人民共和國的漢族（即「中國人民」）從來也沒有擁有過香港，試問又如何「收回」香港？<br />\n<br />\n因此，中華人民共和國取得香港的土地應該形容為「兼併」或「呑併」。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>不平等條約無效論是謊言</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如兩國以和平條約（Peace Treaty）終止戰爭，而某些領土由一國割讓予另一國，則在國際法中亦被視為透過割讓（Cession）而取得主權。過去的國際法觀點認為，以戰爭解決國與國之間的爭議屬國家的權利，而「和平條約」的作用是令交戰雙方以某些條款（包括部份領土的轉讓）為代價以終止戰爭。因此，按照「時空性原則」，1842年及1860年割讓香港島及九龍半島均符合當時的國際法。<br />\n<br />\n國際法中，領土的轉讓只有是否合法，而沒有平等不平等。<br />\n<br />\n在中華人民共和國成為國家之前，英國已經從清帝國手中符合國際法地取得香港的主權。另一方面，中華人民共和國亦從來沒有繼承過清帝國的仼何權益。因此，《中英聯合聲明》中所謂「對香港恢復行使主權」的「恢復」根本無從談起，並且只是一個猜想。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cbwr6sW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbwr6sW.png&h=7ee87500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPAHEN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPAHEN9.png&h=e166e8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知情不報者 你地都係半個兇手！<br />\n你唯一可以做就係站出黎 講個真相比全香港市民聽！ ！ 還死者一個清白！</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肛犬：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n別再喱係電視後面，敢就走出黎攞出CCTV之類証據黎証明831冇人死冇人重傷囉仆街共狗！！！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/05/104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2F104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg&h=7d68f7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必問：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾倍OT收，係咪仲要&quot;好合理要屌埋女示者&quot;咁辛苦？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，鷹犬全鎖；<br />\n<br />\n有錯企定，即決勿拖！<br />\n<br />\n民主斬件，仲當我傻！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，未贏收科？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span></span></span><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除非你係個班那埋護照旁身嘅扮民霸權，永續利益獨賣囉！！！